             double w,

             int lives,

        Enemy constructor which creates an Enemy object with the given position size, and lives.
        Parameters:
        x - double value of the enemy's x-position.
        y - double value of the enemy's y-position.
        w - double value of the enemy's width.
        h - double value of the enemy's height.
        lives - int value of the enemy's lives.
        boost - double value of the enemy's boost value (when the player presses the up-arrow).
